#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:156
msgid ""
"When enabled, the session manager will start the required applications for "
"screen readers and magnifiers."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ຕົວຈັດການເຊດຊັນຈະເລີ່ມແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຈຳເປັນສຳລັບເຄື່ອງອ່ານໜ້າຈໍ ແລະ ເຄື່ອງຂະຫຍາຍໜ້າຈໍ."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:173
msgid "_Enable assistive technologies"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ງານເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ(_E)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:195
msgid "Start With Session"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນພ້ອມກັບເຊດຊັນ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:230
msgid "Assistive technologies will be available the next time you login"
msgstr "ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຈະພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານໃນຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປທີ່ເຈົ້າເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:269
msgid "No AT-SPI provider was found on your system"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການ AT-SPI ໃນລະບົບຂອງເຈົ້າ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:292
msgid "Assistive _Technologies"
msgstr "ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ(_T)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:324
msgid ""
"When enabled, modifier keys (such as Control, Alt, and Shift) do not need to"
" be held down (they can be pressed and then released) when multiple keys "
"would normally need to be pressed at the same time."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ປຸ່ມປັບປ່ຽນ (ເຊັ່ນ Control, Alt, ແລະ Shift) ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງກົດຄ້າງໄວ້ (ສາມາດກົດແລ້ວປ່ອຍໄດ້) ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ປົກກະຕິຕ້ອງກົດຫຼາຍປຸ່ມພ້ອມກັນ."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:347
msgid "_Use sticky keys"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມຄ້າງ(_U)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:375
msgid "_Lock sticky keys"
msgstr "ລັອກປຸ່ມຄ້າງ(_L)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:379
msgid ""
"When selected, modifier keys (such as Control, Alt, and Shift) will remain "
"locked in the pressed state if they are pressed twice in a row, until "
"pressed again once"
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກ, ປຸ່ມປັບປ່ຽນ (ເຊັ່ນ Control, Alt, ແລະ Shift) ຈະຖືກລັອກຄ້າງໄວ້ຖ້າກົດສອງຄັ້ງຕິດຕໍ່ກັນ, ຈົນກວ່າຈະກົດອີກຄັ້ງໜຶ່ງ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:392
msgid "Disable sticky keys if two keys are _pressed"
msgstr "ປິດໃຊ້ປຸ່ມຄ້າງຖ້າກົດສອງປຸ່ມພ້ອມກັນ(_P)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:396
msgid ""
"When selected, the \"sticky keys\" feature will be disabled if two keys are "
"pressed simultaneously"
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກ, ຄຸນສົມບັດ \"ປຸ່ມຄ້າງ\" ຈະຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານຖ້າມີການກົດສອງປຸ່ມພ້ອມກັນ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:431
msgid "Sticky Keys"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຄ້າງ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:461
msgid ""
"To help prevent accidental keystrokes, slow keys requires that a key is held"
" for a certain minimum amount of time before the keystroke will be accepted."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍປ້ອງກັນການກົດປຸ່ມໂດຍບໍ່ຕັ້ງໃຈ, ປຸ່ມຊ້າຈະກຳນົດໃຫ້ຕ້ອງກົດປຸ່ມຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນໄລຍະເວລາໃດໜຶ່ງກ່ອນທີ່ລະບົບຈະຮັບຮູ້ການກົດປຸ່ມນັ້ນ."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:484
msgid "Use slow _keys"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມຊ້າ(_K)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:513
msgid "Acceptance _delay:"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າການຍອມຮັບ(_D):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:527
msgid ""
"The amount of time, in milliseconds, that must elapse before a keystroke "
"will be accepted"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາ (ເປັນມິນລີວິນາທີ) ທີ່ຕ້ອງຜ່ານໄປກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຍອມຮັບການກົດປຸ່ມ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:563
msgid "Slow Keys"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຊ້າ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:593
msgid ""
"To help prevent accidental multiple keystrokes, bounce keys imposes a "
"minimum delay between keystrokes."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍປ້ອງກັນການກົດປຸ່ມຊ້ຳໂດຍບໍ່ຕັ້ງໃຈ, ປຸ່ມດີດຈະກຳນົດໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າຕ່ຳສຸດລະຫວ່າງການກົດປຸ່ມ."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:616
msgid "Use _bounce keys"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມດີດ(_B)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:645
msgid "K_eystroke delay:"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າການກົດປຸ່ມ(_E):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:659
msgid "The amount of time, in milliseconds, required between keystrokes"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາ (ເປັນມິນລີວິນາທີ) ທີ່ຕ້ອງການລະຫວ່າງການກົດປຸ່ມ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:695
msgid "Bounce Keys"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມດີດ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:714
msgid "Keyboa_rd"
msgstr "ຄີບອດ(_R)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:746
msgid ""
"When enabled, the mouse pointer can be controlled using the keyboard number "
"pad."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ສາມາດຄວບຄຸມຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌ໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ແຜງປຸ່ມຕົວເລກເທິງຄີບອດ."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:769
msgid "_Use mouse emulation"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການຈຳລອງເມົາສ໌(_U)"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:773
msgid ""
"When selected, the mouse pointer can be controlled using the keyboard number"
" pad"
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກ, ສາມາດຄວບຄຸມຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌ໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ແຜງປຸ່ມຕົວເລກເທິງຄີບອດ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:801
#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:871
#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:913
msgid "msec"
msgstr "ມິນລີວິນາທີ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:812
msgid ""
"The time, in milliseconds, between the initial key press and first repeated "
"motion event"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາ (ເປັນມິນລີວິນາທີ) ລະຫວ່າງການກົດປຸ່ມຄັ້ງທຳອິດ ແລະ ການເລີ່ມເຄື່ອນທີ່ຊ້ຳ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:829
msgid "_Acceleration delay:"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າການເລັ່ງ(_A):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:842
msgid "R_epeat interval:"
msgstr "ໄລຍະຫ່າງການຊ້ຳ(_E):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:854
msgid "The time, in milliseconds, between repeated motion events"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາ (ເປັນມິນລີວິນາທີ) ລະຫວ່າງເຫດການເຄື່ອນທີ່ຊ້ຳ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:883
msgid "Acceleration t_ime:"
msgstr "ເວລາໃນການເລັ່ງ(_I):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:895
msgid "The time, in milliseconds, to get to maximum speed"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາ (ເປັນມິນລີວິນາທີ) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ບັນລຸຄວາມໄວສູງສຸດ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:925
msgid "Ma_ximum speed:"
msgstr "ຄວາມໄວສູງສຸດ(_X):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:937
msgid "The maximum pointer speed after acceleration"
msgstr "ຄວາມໄວສູງສຸດຂອງຕົວຊີ້ຫຼັງຈາກການເລັ່ງ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:955
msgid "pixels/sec"
msgstr "ພິກເຊລ/ວິນາທີ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:967
msgid "Acceleration _profile:"
msgstr "ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ການເລັ່ງ(_P):"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:979
msgid "The ramp used to reach maximum pointer speed"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບການເພີ່ມຄວາມໄວເພື່ອບັນລຸຄວາມໄວສູງສຸດຂອງຕົວຊີ້"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:1025
msgid "Mouse Emulation"
msgstr "ການຈຳລອງເມົາສ໌"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:1055
msgid ""
"Bind a keyboard shortcut to xfce4-find-cursor to get visual feedback of the "
"mouse pointer's current location."
msgstr "ກຳນົດປຸ່ມລັດໃຫ້ກັບ xfce4-find-cursor ເພື່ອເບິ່ງຕຳແໜ່ງປັດຈຸບັນຂອງຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌."

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:1072
msgid "Show location of pointer on keypress"
msgstr "ສະແດງຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງຕົວຊີ້ເມື່ອກົດປຸ່ມ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:1094
msgid "Find Cursor"
msgstr "ຊອກຫາເຄີເຊີ"

#: common/resources/accessibility-dialog.glade:1113
msgid "_Mouse"
msgstr "ເມົາສ໌(_M)"

